# User skill library

The repo root has `.skills`, a symlink to `~/.skills`, maintained by `pnpm run skills:link` and by template sync.

The same library is reachable as `home` under `.cursor/skills/`, `.codex/skills/`, and `.agent/skills/` (each `home` symlink points at repo `.skills`) so Codex, Google Antigravity, and other tools stay aligned.

When work matches packaged guidance in that tree, read the relevant `SKILL.md` (and any referenced scripts or data) under `.skills/` instead of guessing. Template-owned skills remain in sibling folders under those `skills` directories (not under `home`).
